[55:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'doing is helping you stand up a Docker container on demand. That\'s all it is. So I\'ve set it up to go inside this Warpy Sheets directory. And in this mode, I can just interface with that cloud environment if I want to. And it\'s'

[56:03] [scene:talk]
